The paper proposes a method for unsupervised domain adaptation using deep clustering and regularization techniques. The main focus is on machine learning and computer vision applications, which are typically covered by the cs.LG, cs.CV, and cs.AI sub-categories. The paper also involves natural language processing (NLP) tasks, which are covered by the cs.CL sub-category. Additionally, the paper uses neural networks, which are covered by the cs.NE sub-category.
